    "The cosmic web that connects you is woven from threads of shared purpose and mirrored longing. You arrived in each other's lives not by chance but by the accumulated momentum of everything that came before. Honour what you have — tend to it, protect it, and watch it become something timeless.",
    "Few connections carry this quality of inevitability. The universe conspired across time and distance to bring your specific energies together. What you build from this point forward echoes beyond this single lifetime. You are each other's greatest teacher, and your classroom is the love you share.",
